1. Create a new directory for your project and navigate to it using the command line.
mkdir real-time-chat-app
cd real-time-chat-app
2. Initialize a new Node.js project: Run the following command in the project directory to create a new package.json file.
npm init -y
3.Install the required dependencies: Install Socket.IO packages by running the following command.
npm install express socket.io
4.Create code
index.js, index.html, style.css
5. Run server
node index.js